{"tid":628643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 明報整左警察犯罪專板出黎","createTime":"2018-04-14T05:10:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T07:38:57.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1322,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"6281f05f77b2b44848497d7be26f4bc601db3d21","tid":628643,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/130912_980cefac02ca75a08115acaa84757611.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F130912_980cefac02ca75a08115acaa84757611.png&h=8017b029&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1a97513eeec65fa7ce7e656de41197aebe8d2f5","tid":628643,"uid":64345,"like":347,"dislike":4,"score":343,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:16:38.000Z","msg":"方便排版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n年尾整本警隊犯罪年鑑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0696b195121982a5134b7ed47de8e91fceacbc","tid":628643,"uid":5195,"like":86,"dislike":1,"score":85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:16:44.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】警隊人員近年發生多宗嚴重操守事故，如本周初法院審理一宗個案，涉及一名商業罪案調查科警長去年7月休班期間，在港鐵太子站勒索一名涉嫌非禮男子，要求對方支付1萬元換取不被拘捕，被控勒索罪及盜竊罪，以至一些涉及偷拍女子裙底案，到這宗執勤警員涉偷取妓女銀包內現金等。有資深警官表示，留意到近年警務人員涉及休班時犯案趨勢有所變化，由舊日多被指涉不法分子賄賂勾當等，轉至愈來愈多涉及個人操守行為，警隊宜正視檢視背後成因。<br />\n<br />\n有警官表示，警務人員熟知法律，如犯案至被捕，有理由相信已非初犯，故警隊內部有必要檢視近年警務人員犯案的模式及趨勢，以作防範，並改良訓練以減低相關案件出現。該警官稱，近年警務工作內容變化大，有需要探討方向，包括檢視警務人員在生活及工作上遇到什麼問題及壓力，以致行為上的偏差。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，去年12月22日晚上，54歲休班警員在深水埗店舖內涉拿走一對價值29元的耳筒，未有付款離開，遭職員發現報警，以涉嫌盜竊拘捕該名休班警員。另外，去年法庭審理一宗個案，亦提及中年商人相約16 歲私影少女拍照，其間在私家車內非禮對方，有休班警涉伙商人付錢予事主圖令對方銷案"},{"pid":"4687066af4cd6078a8429c4b2d036cdedc39f6b4","tid":628643,"uid":81795,"like":2,"dislike":23,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:22:55.000Z","msg":"🙈有咁小咩，"},{"pid":"644cba51afdd5bc42526e386c5b99d972ef46961","tid":628643,"uid":47311,"like":90,"dislike":1,"score":89,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:24:21.000Z","msg":"又係佔中蝴蝶效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aebd93f4162fed1278dfc3be63dacb033bcaddcd","tid":628643,"uid":149879,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:24:31.000Z","msg":"得分欄嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b3ef0a91a7100bba2d6db328d9b321e09bc46c","tid":628643,"uid":123774,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:24:32.000Z","msg":"應該搵人做個database <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e58ce10ca3933a8ee6c5756fffbd143faa76ea","tid":628643,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:25:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da3b62930fac0aeddfeafe30d37a74de2af72dc","tid":628643,"uid":5320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:25:39.000Z","msg":"差人做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67e1f742c002e0720cb78a3a9a3e4c4456461ed7","tid":628643,"uid":141151,"like":186,"dislike":0,"score":186,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:26:46.000Z","msg":"A版港聞<br />\nB版財經<br />\nC版娛樂<br />\nD版警察"},{"pid":"326e019f07204ab5039e9854e96e264b14cc2cff","tid":628643,"uid":139224,"like":89,"dislike":2,"score":87,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/133320_73616983cc61c41963697620617f7346.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F133320_73616983cc61c41963697620617f7346.jpeg&h=a4629912&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d423f9f45278bdc203f9bcfb43ff21d1dce54b7","tid":628643,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T05:35:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"907e2d0bb0f2eef212a543fa78d5131d77b868d1","tid":628643,"uid":2