名休班警務人員。兩人現時已獲准保釋候查，須於本月上旬向警方報到。案件交由油尖警區重案組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊定必嚴正處理<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880b4fbba34e3a019a949faaedafc6fed1118dcd","tid":628643,"uid":87433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6556ea6c2e9802339fc010e2747892122f1849cb","tid":628643,"uid":2671,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T07:50:25.000Z","msg":"有無人集資出本香港差佬犯罪記錄？ 幾萬蚊我都資助到嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:01:15.000Z","msg":"1. 孤獨探戈 幾萬<br />\n2."},{"pid":"1d290a8d50ed52df92eedcae1c5099c4fab8427b","tid":628643,"uid":120348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038f12d5be2227a33aa8d956359ad648f1244c20","tid":628643,"uid":138613,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:09:25.000Z","msg":"佢地咁排板可以係每段新聞嘅最後加個箭嘴<br />\n<br />\n指住呢段字<br />\n&quot;警方表示，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊定必嚴正處理&quot;<br />\n<br />\n咁就慳到好多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}